police station (tbh, I had already thought about this ages ago)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">But, please be patient, I still need to finish this frat boy series, and I have a list of requests (yes, Selpedretti, I didn't forget about your boyfriend's bots 🤭)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Last but not least, <br>I would like to welcome new followers, yaaayy, I love you all</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"><strong> </strong>💜</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 281px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_221cc14e-a298-4c9c-bbaf-128c3d8f8d80.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 644px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_ee2e4e5b-4c2b-4b15-bd78-e6b51ac08eac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">This is the <strong>fourth</strong> bot of the </span><strong>KΑΣ</strong>'s<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">frat boys.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">Well, the name itself says all about the series. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">Frat, fresh, young, and dumb boys who don't think twice about breaking your heart </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">or maybe being the love of your life.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 720px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4397885